<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7624111>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3A–J. Gongylonema aguilarense sp. nov. A, Cephalic end female, en face view.B, Anterior end holotype male, lateral view. C, Vulva and vagina, female, lateral view. D, Posterior end holotype male, ventral view. E, Spicules and gubernaculum male, dorsal view. F, Tail tip holotype male, ventral view. G, Embryonated egg, lateral view. H, Proximal end right spicule, lateral view. I, Distal end left spicule, lateral view. J, Posterior end female, lateral view. Scale bars: Figs. 3A, 3E, 3F, 3H, 3I = 20µm. Figs. 3B–3D, 3G, 3J = 50µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7624111/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

